snippet.textDisplay:
Salah needs to leave the Reds right after the League title, and what he gave them is sufficient for them to reach this current position
Because Salah no longer gets the appreciation he really deserves, no matter how creative he was, or even the most important keys to winning in most games for Liverpool .. I also believe that the Liverpool fans are no longer aware of Salah's value and will know it with great regret when they lose him.
-----------------------------
My friends ..
In short and clearly ..
Where was Liverpool's position in the league and without any tournaments with Manny, Firmino and the great Coutinho and most of the current players and under the leadership of Klopp two years before the arrival of Salah !!
Where is the Liverpool team now, and how many championships did it get, after the talented Salah joined them !!
Important information ..
Liverpool club has been getting the best offers from the largest international sponsoring companies due to the huge presence of Salah on social media everywhere.
- I hope Salah will go to Manchester United and continue in the English league and prove once again his presence and accomplishments with them, to respond to everyone -

snippet.textDisplay: I love Inside Anfield. The little details make it.......anyone notice Harvey Elliot meeting his mini-me, also, bless him, Salah checking out his own image on the wall.
